cat << EOF
Ksorcery is a KDE frontend for sorcery.  It allows you to browse your spells' DETAILS and also you can cast, dispel, or summon spells.

Note: sometimes it will not work until you run the command "kbuildsycoca", this fixes something that it needs within the kde framework.
